    "root_cause": "Product Master's sync neared its SLA ceiling (see Expected LRJ catalogue) and tipped over due to an unplanned new-SKU batch, and Ecommerce's publish DAG has zero tolerance built in - it triggers strictly on upstream DAG success signal.",
    "business_impact": "New product launches scheduled for 9am go live 2 hours late on the ecommerce site, a directly measurable revenue-timing impact.",
    "resolution": "Decouple catalog publish from full Product Master completion by publishing incrementally per completed batch using Airflow Datasets."
